I craft
experiences that balance form, function, and feasibility. With 6+ years of experience and
background in Engineering and UX Design, I understand both
code and
creativity. I blend
curiosity,
strategic thinking, and a dash of
playfulness to transform pixels into problem-solving
prototypes. Whether it's a startup's first MVP
or a global enterprise
dashboard, my
focus is always on
delighting users and driving measurable
business growth.
